item.title: About
item.description: Hello ! I’m Minezeratul , a simple student , major in Computer Science and focus on Java. I like playing ping-pong , CS:GO , watching movies , reading novels and so on. For most of the time, I may do some practices on Leetcode , pick one book from my shelf or play ping-pong with my roommate. In my spare time , IT’S TIME FOR girlfriend!!! Haha. We will explore some unknown restaurants , find the good dishes hidden in the alley.
